change file libpurple/protocols/jabber/iq.c
compile
copy libjabber.so.0.0.0 to /usr/lib/purple-2/

specify software name in ~/.purple/nick_domain.name
specify software version in ~/.purple/nick_domain.version

For jid's without these two files, version requests are skipped,
which is OK (e.g., gtalk does so).

